And the weight of the machine is thirty-five tons.

529
00:39:51,000 --> 00:39:54,000
Dexta makînê, hefsed û pêncî ton e.
 
The pressure of the machine is seven hundred and fifty tons.

530
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:55,000
