Hello partner.

535
00:40:03,000 --> 00:40:04,000
Ahlan wa sahlan.
 
Welcome.

536
00:40:04,000 --> 00:40:05,000
Em te nas bikin?
 
May we know you?

537
00:40:05,000 --> 00:40:06,000
Mistefa.
 
Mustafa.

538
00:40:06,000 --> 00:40:08,000
Mistefa, tu çi li vî karî dikî?
 
Mustafa, what do you do in this job?

539
