Do you work tomorrow as well?

545
00:40:15,000 --> 00:40:18,000
Sibe în e, sibe hes e.
 
Tomorrow is Friday, tomorrow is rest.

546
00:40:18,000 --> 00:40:21,000
Ê qolê be şerîk, sarxweş.
 
May it be easy partner, cheers.

547
